Religion is a good thing.  See, multiple people can do more than individuals.  Institutions which sway multiple people to the same goal are more likely to succeed than individual efforts.  This means religions which encourage their members to be productive citizens and to convert others and to not practice birth control will be more plentiful and successful than organizations which do not promote these things.<br>
<br>
